Siebert U(1), Sroczynski G, Hillemanns P, Engel J, Stabenow R, Stegmaier C, 
Voigt K, Gibis B, Hölzel D, Goldie SJ.

Author information:
(1)Department of Public Health, Medical Decision Making and Health Technology 
